{"tid":329852,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會買盧斯達新書 獨立屠場 ？","createTime":"2017-07-20T16:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T13:11:57.000Z","uid":30807,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"515a9294c40480db6ad231167c4ddb8706658d91","tid":329852,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T16:43:40.000Z","msg":"無待堂<br />\n7月19日 15:47 &middot; <br />\n//感謝李怡為《獨立屠場》作序//<br />\n<br />\n李怡：盧斯達以無待堂的論政網誌在多年前崛起，我就留意及閱讀。後來知道他那時還是年輕學生，更感驚異。他知識廣博，觀察敏銳，見解獨特，想像豐富，常在人們對一些社會問題感困擾時，提出切中要害的看法。讀其文，很難相信是時下追求速食文化的年輕人的寫作。<br />\n<br />\n獨持異見，當然會引起爭議。他文章的論點我也常有些不同意見。但只要不是立場主導，必須珍惜寫作人的這種銳利、敢言。讀到與自己意見不同的文章，是一種收穫。許多網絡聚集意見一致的同溫層，其實是相當無趣的事。<br />\n<br />\n本書是盧斯達在本土意識陷於低潮時的沉思，值得細讀。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20121187_1416878098397931_3282165694508508039_o.jpg?oh=d2a2eb8df01a7e6790f190b4e7f5b0cd&amp;oe=59FE066F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20121187_1416878098397931_3282165694508508039_o.jpg%3Foh%3Dd2a2eb8df01a7e6790f190b4e7f5b0cd%26oe%3D59FE066F&h=785e89f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n書展簽名<br />\n<br />\n【地點】<br />\nHall 1C（書刊館）1C-C04-16攤位<br />\n【時間】<br />\n星期四(20號) 8:00pm之後<br />\n星期六(22) 6:00pm 之後<br />\n星期日(23) 6:00pm之後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我今晚買左，見到好多索女女問堂主拎簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9c591f612258604a5da2542d2e4d540f0473b8","tid":329852,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T18:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38048bbdeed3892f91ee78dbc7d2ad65ca9ab964","tid":329852,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:44:27.000Z","msg":"買ed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bc8ae0200d05e5ab946c770186f41d04219d35","tid":329852,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買ed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇拎簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e4c6c9727151b7913fb15dab634cdfa33e7b61","tid":329852,"uid":37081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:39:39.000Z","msg":"撐堂主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db49a1f78faa6888ba8672ede188f9e685c24bcf","tid":329852,"uid":30807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撐堂主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲買左毓民新書<br />\n年初一記事(收益唔洗扣三成行政費捐比旺角抗議者)<br />\n兩本書上下 講67暴動<br />\n本土觀點的香港源流史"},{"pid":"2a2d5138f9883dfcac951f01ea8bf4ceae2ed892","tid":329852,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc403239ee2992b9eb57c95f592ec637afb2768","tid":329852,"uid":25329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"買左"},{"pid":"54c56a1886e8ba9b5d56371fb3f46d3053fc0ce6","tid":329852,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:02:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買左</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5523d39108df3eaf9f74601b789d033b9df11435","tid":329852,"uid":20282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:12:08.000Z","msg":"買左"},{"pid":"5303c1348946e80e5f0985d77f15eef18c4642a3","tid":329852,"uid":42002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi